examples.translation: I tried, but I did't succeed.

etymology:
From Ottoman Turkish باشارمق (başarmak), related to باش (baş). Ultimately from Proto-Turkic *baĺč.
Cognate with Old Turkic [script needed] (başgar-), Turkmen başarmak, Uzbek bosharmoq, Kyrgyz башкаруу (başkaruu), Kazakh басқару (basqaru), etc.
